1
00:00:01,400 --> 00:00:06,480
I'm Mohamed Ali Keshavarz,
the actor who plays the director.

2
00:00:06,520 --> 00:00:08,360
The other actors
were hired on location.

3
00:00:09,400 --> 00:00:12,000
We're in Koker,
about 400 kilometers

4
00:00:12,701 --> 00:00:14,951
no, 350 kilometers
north of Teheran,

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:19,280
where an earthquake
destroyed everything last year.

6
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:21,000
The girls are hungry,
they've still got a long way to go.

7
00:00:21,001 --> 00:00:23,000
Can we speed it up a bit?

8
00:00:24,701 --> 00:00:27,500
We have come to this rebuilt school

9
00:00:27,501 --> 00:00:29,001
to choose a young actress.

10
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:38,000
I'm sorry, I'm late.

11
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:49,920
What's your name?

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:50,920
Mehri Ziai

13
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:55,080
- What's your name?
- Sima Ali Mohammadi

14
00:00:55,081 --> 00:00:57,000
- What?
- Sima Ali Mohammadi

15
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:00,280
- And you?
- Leyla Naghipour.

16
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:05,000
- You, what's your name?
- Tahereh Ladanian.

17
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,720
Mrs. Shiva,
note down this girl's address.

18
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:11,480
- Your address?
- Near the Lakeh bazaar.

19
00:01:11,481 --> 00:01:12,480
- Your name?
- Tahereh Ladanian

20
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,840
- Your address
Near the Lakeh bazaar.

21
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:19,560
- You, what's your name?
- Fariba Jafari

22
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:23,000
- What class?
3rd Year literature.

23
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,280
- Mrs. Shiva, note down her name too.

24
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,920
- And you?
- Nazila Khadem

25
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,920
Mrs. Shiva, note her name.

26
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:35,760
- Your address?
- I haven't got a real address

27
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,520
But where do you live?

28
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,520
Rostam-Abbad, in Jalalye.

29
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,000
It's cold.

30
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:44,120
What's your name?

31
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,080
Zinat Hassanpour

32
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:50,600
You're all out of line!

33
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,000
Where will you show it?

34
00:01:53,001 --> 00:01:55,000
You're filming us...
Oh, what does it matter?

35
00:01:55,001 --> 00:01:57,001
You won't show it.

36
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,320
- You mean, on TV?
- Yes

37
00:02:01,321 --> 00:02:02,320
You're right.

38
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,120
But is that any reason
not to film?

39
00:02:05,121 --> 00:02:07,080
Aren't you going to show it to us?

40
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:11,680
Your last film went out on Channel 2,
which we can't get here. Why bother?

41
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:14,640
What do you say?
Do we film or not?

42
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,400
We film!

43
00:02:16,401 --> 00:02:17,401
We film!
But you'll have to show it!

44
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,320
Yes, you'll have to show it!

45
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,120
- What's your name again?
- Tahereh.

46
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,600
Tahereh what?

47
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,680
Poursadeghi

48
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,320
Mrs. Shiva, note her name too.

49
00:02:28,321 --> 00:02:30,000
Say your name again.

50
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,600
Your address?

51
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,960
You, what's your name?

52
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,040
Zahra Djenab.

53
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,200
- From where?
- Rostam-Abbad.

54
00:02:41,201 --> 00:02:42,040
- How old are you?
- 15.

55
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:43,440
15?

56
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:47,800
Mrs. Shiva, note down her name.

57
00:02:47,801 --> 00:02:48,920
- Your name?
- Zahra Dejnab.

58
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,600
- Your address?
- Rostam-Abbad, in Koker.

